r />\n但無捱過果段時期 係有d可惜</blockquote><br />\n本身唔夾咩，咁易就嘈？"},{"pid":"0659885332bb25814341c9e729b4ca90e30f4d90","tid":430314,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T03:14:19.000Z","msg":"真係難啲"},{"pid":"418bee526e04225150c040ccf7696fadf6ebb457","tid":430314,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T03:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159582e8c13c7ed174cce1aef4ddbbdf6d3b0a49","tid":430314,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T03:14:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>啱啱散時有好憎過佢，到宜家我都話俾自己聽我對佢已經無感覺，但係見到一啲同佢好似樣嘅人，又會忍唔出喊出嚟，自從佢，我無再拍過拖。</blockquote><br />\n散左幾耐</blockquote><br />\n年幾</blockquote><br />\n我都試過遇到個好似佢<br />\n但好快抽離到"},{"pid":"a938ed75d51a4f179d8a6dd8e67cad1660b0f9b6","tid":430314,"uid":20538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T08:12:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>啱啱散時有好憎過佢，到宜家我都話俾自己聽我對佢已經無感覺，但係見到一啲同佢好似樣嘅人，又會忍唔出喊出嚟，自從佢，我無再拍過拖。</blockquote><br />\n散左幾耐</blockquote><br />\n年幾</blockquote><br />\n我都試過遇到個好似佢<br />\n但好快抽離到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見唔到就無事 一見到就喊到仆街"},{"pid":"78a35c670d3659e455141107030bd2cc90b1c070","tid":430314,"uid":9647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:05:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c508c34e44f41f3a68be5a0fa7deca12b90382d","tid":430314,"uid":143394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔再ff 之後<br />\n發覺已經冇左果份<span style=\"color: red;\">汁</span>著<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942863ee47ad3218959252fe22cfcbc7103f692e","tid":430314,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T14:35:03.000Z","msg":"<blockqu